MasterChef Canada - Season 1, Episode 5




Where's the Beef?

The home cooks face their second Mystery Box Challenge and this time victory rests on a lot of creativity and a little bit of elbow-grease. They each have one meat grinder and a wide array of fresh protein at their disposal: bison, lamb, turkey, kangaroo... everything but beef.

Their goal: to make the perfect gourmet burger.




Original Air Date: 17-Feb-2014
